dialogue.name: no_one
dialogue.string: And through the power of song, Girlfriend was able to write down the lyrics to her very own love song for her darling Boyfriend.

dialogue.name: no_one
dialogue.string: The girls excitedly ask to see what Girlfriend had come up with, so she handed them the paper with all the lyrics written on it.

dialogue.name: no_one
dialogue.string: With much anticipation, the girls began to read, and-

dialogue.name: no_one
dialogue.string: -their expressions slowly morphed into ones of shock and confusion.

dialogue.name: monika
dialogue.string: "...I wasn't expecting you to write something so... explicit-"

dialogue.name: natsuki
dialogue.string: "Eugh, eww!!! Why did you write that?! I don't need to know what you and your boyfriend do at night!"

dialogue.name: yuri
dialogue.string: "I'm... curious as to what inspired you to write down several verses about 'The blood of your enemies'-"

dialogue.name: sayori
dialogue.string: "Eheheh... ehhhhh... maybe next time, try to keep things school appropriate-"
